<paragraph blockId="51.[151,1436,152,418]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis box="[198,322,152,177]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Etymology</emphasis>
. A latinized form of the proper noun Solomon in reference to the 
<collectingCountry box="[1126,1323,152,178]" name="Solomon Islands" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Solomon Islands</collectingCountry>
in which this genus is quite diverse. The genus name should be considered male in gender.
</paragraph>
